cs.LO, cs.CR, cs.PL, cs.FL, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the development of a logic for expressing hyperproperties, which are properties that relate different executions of a system to each other. This is a topic that is relevant to several areas of computer science, including logic (cs.LO), cryptography (cs.CR), programming languages (cs.PL), formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
